          <td width="26%"><span class="style1"> <p><strong>Community contest</strong>: Design a draft SCD logo! Contest details to follow</p> </span></td> 
          <td width="74%"><p align="center"><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px"><b><font color="#000066">GeoPRISMS Implementation Workshop:<br> Subduction Cycles and Deformation</font></b></span></p> <p align="center" style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"><b><font color="#660000">Austin</font><font color="#660000">, TX<br> January 5 - 7, 2011</font></b></p> <p align="center" style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"><b><span style="color: #FF0000; font-size: 16px">Deadline for applications: October 8, 2010</span><br> <br> </b></p></td> 
